<main id=content role=main>
<p itemprop=description>A guy that does things, and thinks that having a reason for doing so is largely overrated. (Co-)founder of <a href=//deidee.com/ lang=nl translate=no>deIdee</a> <i>&amp;</i> <a href=//dekkerchen.com/ translate=no>Dekker Chen</a>, <i>et al</i>. Member of the <a href=//awesomeblackninjadevils.com/ itemprop=performer itemscope itemtype=http://schema.org/MusicGroup>Awesome Black Ninja Devils</a>, and <a href=//fragile-minds.com/>Fragile Minds</a>. Living with <abbr title=girlfriend>gf</abbr> <a href=//myrthedeluxe.com/>Myrthe Deluxe</a> + <abbr title=dog>&#x1f415;</abbr> + <abbr title=cat>&#x1f408;</abbr>.</p>
<p>Featured projects (in alphabetical order): <a href=//allrgb.com/ translate=no>all<abbr title="Red Green Blue">rgb</abbr></a>, <a href=//applebeardcondom.com/>Apple Beard Condom</a> (with <a class=n href=//matthijsbooij.nl/ lang=nl translate=no>Matthijs Booij</a>), <a href=//letteretters.com/ lang=nl translate=no>L&nbsp;E&nbsp;T&nbsp;T&nbsp;E&nbsp;R E&nbsp;T&nbsp;T&nbsp;E&nbsp;R&nbsp;S</a> (with 11 designers), <a href=//mimesia.com/ translate=no>Mimesia</a>, <a href=//mopitandmoveon.org/>Mop It &amp; Move On</a> (with <a class=n href=//www.davidbenque.com/ lang=fr translate=no>David Benqué</a>), <a href=//mortalkombatkourier.com/ translate=no>Mortal Kombat Kourier</a>, <a href=//neoaestheticism.com/ translate=no>Neo-æstheticism</a>, <a href=//netplasticism.com/ translate=no>Netplasticism</a>, <a href=//onzinnen.nl/ lang=nl translate=no>Onzinnen</a>, <a href=//periodicsystem.org/>Periodic System of the Elements</a>, <a href=//proseccofriday.com/>Prosecco Friday</a> (with a couple of bubbly friends), <a href=//randomgradients.com/>Random Gradients</a>, <a href=//siteinasecond.nl/>Site in a Second</a>, <a href=//superpositionday.com/>Superposition Day</a>, <a href=//utterlyrandom.com/>Utterly Random</a>…</p>
<p><dfn>Internet art</dfn> (in reverse chronological order): <a href=//spam.world/ itemprop=workPerformed itemscope itemtype=http://schema.org/CreativeWork>Spam World</a>, <a href=//netart.work/ itemprop=workPerformed itemscope itemtype=http://schema.org/CreativeWork translate=no>netart.work</a>, <a href=//everythingisuntrue.com/ itemprop=workPerformed itemscope itemtype=http://schema.org/CreativeWork>Everything is (un)true</a>, <a href=//adhdadhdadhd.com/ itemprop=workPerformed itemscope itemtype=http://schema.org/CreativeWork translate=no><abbr>adhdadhdadhd</abbr></a>, <a href=//thelastworkofart.com/ itemprop=workPerformed itemscope itemtype=http://schema.org/CreativeWork>The Last Work of Art</a>, <a href=//colourandom.com/ itemprop=workPerformed itemscope itemtype=http://schema.org/CreativeWork translate=no>ColouRandom (or Colour and Om)</a>, <a href=//xn--3j8h.ml/ itemprop=workPerformed itemscope itemtype=http://schema.org/CreativeWork translate=no>&#127872;.ml</a>, <a href=//a00ade.com/ itemprop=workPerformed itemscope itemtype=http://schema.org/CreativeWork translate=no>#A00ADE</a>, <a href=//fortheloveofdamienhirst.com/ itemprop=workPerformed itemscope itemtype=http://schema.org/CreativeWork>For The Love of Damien Hirst</a>, <a href=//willekleur.nl/ itemprop=workPerformed itemscope itemtype=http://schema.org/CreativeWork lang=nl translate=no>Willekleur</a>, <a href=//victoryboogiewoogie.com/ itemprop=workPerformed itemscope itemtype=http://schema.org/CreativeWork translate=no>Victory Boogie Woogie&nbsp;.com</a>, <a href=//themostexpensiveworkofart.com/ itemprop=workPerformed itemscope itemtype=http://schema.org/CreativeWork>The Most Expensive Work of Art</a>, <a href=//opencomposition.com/ itemprop=workPerformed itemscope itemtype=http://schema.org/CreativeWork>Open Composition</a>, <a href=//koninklijkekunst.nl/ itemprop=workPerformed itemscope itemtype=http://schema.org/CreativeWork lang=nl>Koninklijke Kunst</a>, <a href=//artficiallyintelligentdesignsystems.com/ itemprop=workPerformed itemscope itemtype=http://schema.org/CreativeWork>Artificially Intelligent Design Systems</a>, <a href=//socledumonad.com/ itemprop=workPerformed itemscope itemtype=http://schema.org/CreativeWork lang=fr>Socle du Monad</a> (sort of broken now), <a href=//compositioni.com/ itemprop=workPerformed itemscope itemtype=http://schema.org/CreativeWork>Composition <var translate=no>i</var></a>, <a href=//thesearchfornotitle.com/ itemprop=workPerformed itemscope itemtype=http://schema.org/CreativeWork>The Search for No Title</a>, <a href=//■.ws/ itemprop=workPerformed itemscope itemtype=http://schema.org/CreativeWork translate=no>■</a>, <a href=//areyougoingtoanswerthisquestionwithno.com/ itemprop=workPerformed itemscope itemtype=http://schema.org/CreativeWork>Are you going to answer this question with “no”?</a>, <a href=//areyougoingtoanswerthisquestionwithyesorno.com/ itemprop=workPerformed itemscope itemtype=http://schema.org/CreativeWork>Are you going to answer this question with yes or no?</a>, <a href=//compositionn.com/ itemprop=workPerformed itemscope itemtype=http://schema.org/CreativeWork>Composition <var translate=no>n</var></a>, <a href=//trahison.be/ itemprop=workPerformed itemscope itemtype=http://schema.org/CreativeWork lang=fr>La trahison de l’Internet</a>…</p>
<p>If you must, you can <a href=//follow.alexanderchristiaanjacob.com/>follow me</a>, <a href=//contact.alexanderchristiaanjacob.com/>contact me</a>, or find more of my stuff at <a href=//acjs.net/ translate=no><abbr>ACJ</abbr>’s</a>. <a href=//alexanderchristiaanjacob.com/ itemprop=url title=Refresh>&#8635;</a></p>
